                "en": "Fast static hosting with no runtime service dependency.",
                "zh-CN": "静态托管速度快，不依赖运行时服务。"
              }
            ]
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "efficiency-mechanisms",
      "title": {
        "en": "Token, Speed, And Readability Mechanisms",
        "zh-CN": "Token、速度与可读性机制"
      },
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "summary",
          "items": [
            {
              "label": {
                "en": "Token discipline",
                "zh-CN": "Token 约束"
              },
              "body": {
                "en": "Agents read and edit compact source JSON while generated HTML remains a publish artifact.",
                "zh-CN": "agent 读取和编辑紧凑源 JSON，生成 HTML 只作为发布产物。"
              }
            },
            {
              "label": {
                "en": "Fast rendering",
                "zh-CN": "快速渲染"
              },
              "body": {
                "en": "Rendering is a local deterministic pass with standard-library Python and no network fetches.",
                "zh-CN": "渲染是本地确定性流程，使用 Python 标准库且不发起网络请求。"
              }
            },
            {
              "label": {
                "en": "Stable review",
                "zh-CN": "稳定审阅"
              },
              "body": {
                "en": "The same JSON source produces the same HTML shell, making visual and textual diffs predictable.",
                "zh-CN": "相同 JSON 源会生成相同 HTML 外壳，让视觉和文本 diff 可预测。"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "table",
          "tableType": "data",
          "headers": [
            {
              "en": "Goal",
              "zh-CN": "目标"
            },
            {
              "en": "How cast-a-doc achieves it",
              "zh-CN": "cast-a-doc 如何实现"
            },
            {
              "en": "Evidence in the system",
              "zh-CN": "系统中的依据"
            }
          ],
          "rows": [
            [
              {
                "en": "Save tokens",
                "zh-CN": "节省 token"
              },
              {
                "en": "Keep semantic source separate from generated HTML; agents can inspect manifest and relevant sections instead of reading the whole page artifact.",
                "zh-CN": "把语义源和生成 HTML 分离；agent 可检查 manifest 和相关 sections，而不是读取整页产物。"
              },
              {
                "en": "JSON source files, manifest.sections, typed blocks, source-refs, files blocks.",
                "zh-CN": "JSON 源文件、manifest.sections、类型化 blocks、source-refs、files blocks。"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "en": "Standardize output",
                "zh-CN": "标准化输出"
              },
              {
                "en": "Schema, component registry, html profile, and shared shell templates constrain what a document can contain.",
                "zh-CN": "schema、组件注册表、HTML profile 和共享 shell 模板约束文档内容。"
              },
              {
                "en": "schemas/doc.schema.json, config/components.json, config/html-profile.json, shell templates.",
                "zh-CN": "schemas/doc.schema.json、config/components.json、config/html-profile.json、shell 模板。"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "en": "Render fast",
                "zh-CN": "快速渲染"
              },
              {
                "en": "Use a single local render pass and inline only the required interaction modules for the active document.",
                "zh-CN": "使用一次本地渲染流程，并只内联当前文档需要的交互模块。"
              },
              {
                "en": "resolve_active_interactions, render_interaction_assets, self-contained HTML.",
                "zh-CN": "resolve_active_interactions、render_interaction_assets、自包含 HTML。"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "en": "Stay agent-readable",
                "zh-CN": "保持 agent 可读"
              },
              {
                "en": "Use explicit ids, registered block types, localized fields, and source references instead of free-form page markup.",
                "zh-CN": "使用显式 id、注册 block type、多语言字段和源引用，而不是自由 HTML 页面标记。"
              },
              {
                "en": "SECTION_ID_RE, validate_block, localizedString, source-refs/files blocks.",
                "zh-CN": "SECTION_ID_RE、validate_block、localizedString、source-refs/files blocks。"
              }
            ]
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "standardization-loop",
      "title": {
        "en": "Standardization Loop",
        "zh-CN": "标准化闭环"
      },
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": {
            "en": "Standardization is enforced at several layers rather than by convention alone. Authors choose from known block types, validators reject unsupported shapes, the renderer emits one shell, visual lint catches rough UI choices, and checked fixtures prevent accidental output drift.",
            "zh-CN": "标准化不是只靠约定，而是在多个层面执行：作者从已知 block type 中选择，校验器拒绝不支持的结构，渲染器输出统一 shell，visual lint 捕获粗糙 UI 选择，fixture 防止输出意外漂移。"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "diagram",
          "kind": "flow",
          "title": {
            "en": "Standardization Feedback Loop",
            "zh-CN": "标准化反馈闭环"
          },
          "downloadName": "standardization-loop",
          "source": {
            "format": "structured-flow",
            "nodes": [
              {
                "id": "contract",
                "label": {
                  "en": "Schema Contract",
                  "zh-CN": "Schema 契约"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "registry",
                "label": {
                  "en": "Component Registry",
                  "zh-CN": "组件注册表"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "renderer",
                "label": {
                  "en": "Renderer Shell",
                  "zh-CN": "渲染器外壳"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "lint",
                "label": {
                  "en": "Validation + Visual Lint",
                  "zh-CN": "校验 + 视觉 lint"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "fixtures",
                "label": {
                  "en": "Checked Fixtures",
                  "zh-CN": "入库 fixtures"
                }
              }
            ],
            "edges": [
              {
                "from": "contract",
                "to": "registry",
                "label": {
                  "en": "allowed blocks",
                  "zh-CN": "允许 blocks"
                }
              },
              {
                "from": "registry",
                "to": "renderer",
                "label": {
                  "en": "render handlers",
                  "zh-CN": "渲染处理器"
                }
              },
              {
                "from": "renderer",
                "to": "lint",
                "label": {
                  "en": "generated HTML",
                  "zh-CN": "生成 HTML"
                }
              },
              {
                "from": "lint",
                "to": "fixtures",
                "label": {
                  "en": "must pass",
                  "zh-CN": "必须通过"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "list",
          "items": [
            {
              "en": "A new block type is not complete until schema, renderer, component registry, example JSON, generated HTML, and fixture validation all agree.",
              "zh-CN": "新的 block type 只有在 schema、renderer、组件注册表、示例 JSON、生成 HTML 和 fixture 校验都一致后才算完成。"
            },
            {
              "en": "Generated HTML is reviewed as output, but source JSON is the compact and structured place where agents should reason.",
              "zh-CN": "生成 HTML 作为输出被审阅，但源 JSON 才是 agent 应该推理的紧凑结构化界面。"
            },
            {
              "en": "Project profile defaults standardize repository-specific tone, locale, links, and asset choices without hiding them from the source document.",
              "zh-CN": "Project profile 默认值统一仓库级语气、语言、链接和资源选择，但不会把它们从源文档中隐藏。"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
